{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Quick, nimble, and efficient apps provide the best user experience on iPhone OS. Learn advanced techniques for optimizing memory usage and making efficient network requests. Get expert instruction on how to use Instruments and other tools to examine your application’s memory footprint, monitor network activity, and track CPU utilization to fine tune application performance. This is the first part of a two part series."}],"kind":"article","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc10-135-advanced-performance-optimization-on-iphone-os-part-1"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"WWDC10","role":"sampleCode","title":"Advanced Performance Optimization on iPhone OS, Part 1","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}]},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC10"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","isActive":true}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC10-135-Advanced-Performance-Optimization-on-iPhone-OS-Part-1"},"sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2010\/135\/","overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex"}},"references":{"WWDC10.jpeg":{"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC10.jpeg"}],"t